# Integration manifest

When `mode: program`, workers must:

1. Read `program/integration/manifest.md` (path from `state.program.integration_manifest`).
2. Cite manifest section in WorkResult summary (e.g. "manifest §Attachment sockets").
3. Do not invent socket names or export settings not in manifest.
